ent-WeaponLaserCannon = laser cannon
    .desc = A heavy duty, high powered laser weapon. Comes with a scope.

ent-WeaponPulseRifle = pulse rife
    .desc = A phased pulse rifle in the 40 watt range, capable of firing a concentrated energy beam or a structure destroying plasma projectile. Its self-recharging nature allows for constant usage in all environments. Usually found in the hands of fighters with an overblown budget.
